{"tid":2059690,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港台高層、署理副廣播處長陳敏娟辭職，9月1日離任。","createTime":"2020-06-11T05:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T05:48:06.000Z","uid":48040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0db9aa1fbd7f95a4f97b3ab8416c9402772cbd19","tid":2059690,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T05:48:06.000Z","msg":"聲稱是健康原因。<br />\n<br />\n陳敏娟早上在港台高層會議上透露，因為健康理由，6月1日向廣播處長提出請辭。<br />\n<br />\n現年58歲的陳敏娟，在港台任職超過30年，港台感謝陳敏娟多年以來的服務及貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n至於陳敏娟辭職後的工作安排，伍曼儀表示，港台會因應運作需要及根據公務員事務規例，安排合適人員署任副廣播處長（節目）的職位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531434-20200611.htm?archive_date=2020-06-11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531434-20200611.htm%3Farchive_date%3D2020-06-11&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRCLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=67462c5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531434-20200611.htm%3Farchive_date%3D2020-06-11&h=4ca4350f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531434-20200611.htm?archive_date=2020-06-11</a><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_OtH-ee5lSw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_OtH-ee5lSw&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRCLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=5dc3eaec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_OtH-ee5lSw</a>"}]}